
Port scanning:
contentious multiple SYN or RST packet in captures
tcp.flags.syn == 1 or tcp.flags.reset == 1

Brute Force Attack on FTP:
FTP response code for login failure
“ftp.response.code==530”

ICMP ping sweep:
icmp.type==8 or icmp.type==0

TCP ping sweep:
tcp.dstport==7

UDP ping sweep:
udp.dstport==7

Null scan:
tcp.flags==0x000

Xmas scans:
tcp.flags==0X029

UDP scan:
icmp.type==3 and icmp.code==3

SYN flood:
tcp.flags.syn == 1 and tcp.flags.ack == 0
